taff on 5th August Strike<br />\n<br />\nContent <br />\nDear Management of ___________,  <br />\n<br />\nAccording to sources as diverse as newspaper headlines (see attached link below) and various discussions on Facebook and web forums, a major strike is expected on 5th August (next Monday), with large scale assembly is also expected in our area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=8f562642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"2ba5955683f64e28294c0ec60acb9cae051a3e7c","tid":1396290,"uid":215487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"又推佢。屌。可唔可以放三上d片上黎"},{"pid":"dcad9151450ba333167cfae02292b0b1512df471","tid":1396290,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"屌過幾多次咪撚post依條撚樣?<br />\n<br />\n樓豬3毛 fack checked <br />\nShow Blocked User - 我係自由閪呀吹咩"},{"pid":"37ed7be8a9bd0c0a5d5185591fdcf1ffba84a88f","tid":1396290,"uid":138598,"like":0,"dislike":0